                ],
                [
                    "description",
                    "RDP lateral movement is Yayo's signature post-access technique at 9 reports — once inside, the actor pivots across Windows hosts using Remote Desktop Protocol authenticated with harvested domain or local credentials. RDP-based movement provides interactive graphical access to additional systems, enabling the actor to explore the victim environment, collect sensitive data, and expand the scope of compromised access for resale or further exploitation."
                ],
